\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 It was only initially after the accident that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well several years after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you have to do to help with him - did you have to help to dress him or things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, me mother did - me mother did that and
 then I did that at the infirmary to - I used to wheel him in this carriage to the infirmary. Well helping anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - younger I was and we had to go to bed about eight o'clock. But later it was nine o'clock and then later it was ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How old would you be when you had to go to bed at eight o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - just - school age. About four or five year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So when you started at school you stayed up til}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15629495\charrsid11173738 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738  nine o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How old would you be when you were allowed to stay up later than that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well after I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your mother or your father put you to bed normally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - when I were very young me father did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your mother ever put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I - I daresay. My father - but we had to put ourselves to bed - a few years after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About how old do you think you'd be when you started putting yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About five or six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you share the bedroom or the bed with anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Me brother. Me brother and I in one bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you had one room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And your parents had the other room?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the other room, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 There wasn't a bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have a bath that you -?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well one of those - zinc baths. There were no bathing houses in those days - in that type of house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How often were you bathed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well when we were young and come in dirty we were bathed every time we were dirty but - several years after, once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How about clean clothes - when did you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well once every week unless we dirtied them. And in the school hol - in the school holidays we - change us oftener.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Which room did you have your meals in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were there any occasions when you might eat in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would it be breakfast perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh we had our breakfast in the - in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You had breakfast in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the other meals, were they regularly in the living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the living room. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But would it sometimes possibly be in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well if there was any repairs to the house we would have to go into the kitchen then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Where did your mother cook - would that be in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the kitchen. In the kitchen and then a - coal fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 The coal fire was in the kitchen was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. It was in the living room. And then she had a bit of a stove - in the - in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 A gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did she have any other appliances like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She didn't have a little gas ring or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well later on we - we got a gas ring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But this was a proper gas cooker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no, not the type that we have today. They're more like a biscuit box affair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Over a gas jet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would she use that for casual use or did she use it regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well she used the gas fire mostly. And then there was open you know to the gas - not gas fire, to the coal fire - there was a oven to it and you did all your cooking - you did most of your cooking in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So she would only used the gas stove occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When was breakfast eaten - did you have a regular time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it - just depended on whether we were going to school or whether we was working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well when you were going to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh we had breakfast at eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would that be your mother and you and your brother and your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 All of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about when you were going to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well we - we used to start at six o'clock in the mornin
g. So we had - a drink of tea before we went out, then we came back for - for breakfast at eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 That would be just you would it and your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well at one time he - when I were started working he hadn't started working. But the same thing applied when he did start work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Your father's working hours were the same all through were they - would he always have breakfast at eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 At home - yes. He didn't have this tea at six o'clock as we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 He would start a bit later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you normally have to eat and drink for your breakfast proper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well for this six o'clock affair we had just had the tea and a biscuit. Then at for breakfast we - had a lot of toast and jam. Sometimes egg.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about when you were going to school - what sort of breakfast did you have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh well, we used to have porridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you all have porridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your father have something different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well he may have had some bacon but - me and me brother, we had this porridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And what to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have different things on certain days such as Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, we had - oh for breakfast, oh we'd have some bacon. For breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 All of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What time did you have your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Twelve o'clock. Between twelve and - half past.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your father come home the same time that you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did he come home for his dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, but he was later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So between twelve and just after it would be dinner for you and -?
