\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Your brother and mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
