 we always had rice pudding to finish up with and - sometimes we'd have a potato pie, sometimes we'd have a - a hot-pot. But we always finished up with a with a pudding - rice pudding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you ever have any different kinds of puddings?
