\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh had to have what - what was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What was your parents attitude if you left something uneaten on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well sometimes we'd have to have it later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If you didn't eat it then it was there next time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. That's right. You couldn't afford to throw it away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they scold you at all if you left it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If there was something 
on the table that you wanted like the salt could you ask somebody to pass it to you or did you have to wait for it to be offered?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No we - we - asked for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If there was enough could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it was very rare. Oh we could have if - if they wanted it but - if it wasn't there then - we'd had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And to sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When we'd all finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You had to wait until everybody finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have to ask then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, just - used to break away then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did the family all sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well me father and mother sat at the table but us two boys when we were young stood up. Stood up at the table - yes. Of course later on we - we sat down but as we were young boys had to stand up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you always have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How was the meal served - was it your mother who served?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, she served out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What wonder would she serve you in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh me father first. Then us two boys. Then she served herself if there's anything left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did she serve you boys in any order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Before you could feed yourselves where did you sit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Oh I expect we'd be in a - one of those high chairs. And then when - when we got running about we'd - perhaps have a little chair and feed ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Before you could feed yourselves did your mother feed you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Or your father?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About how old would you be before you started sitting at the table - would it be as soon as you big enough to sit up properly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
No, we - when we came to the table first we stood up. Then it was - perhaps seven or eight year old - nine year old when we could sit down then. See we sat down. We couldn't reach the table before. That's why we had to stand up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you tell me a bit about your mother - was she an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Well, in the house she was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 For you to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did she show affection very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, while were - while we were good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about your father - was he easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, very easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Easier than your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did he show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, he used to take me to the cricket matches and football matches.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And did you discuss worries with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I don't know I had any worries - up to going to school - to leaving school. Then you had when you started working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would it be your mother or your father you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I never used - I never used to carry me work home. So there were no worries - not for them anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh we had to show respect to 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they bring you up to behave towards your brother in a particular way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. They let - let each of us know that the other was - was a brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you brought up to feel a special sense of responsibility because of his being crippled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, if he was out to - play with the other children I had to keep eye on him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When you were playing did your parents say you should hit back or not if another child hit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No need to tell me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You did automatically?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they approve of this or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did - w
ell it just depends whether the other - the other lads father or mother went round. Then you had to say - shouldn't do that you know. I was only thin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that on the quiet they approved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they expected - they thought we should grow up respectable same as them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they bring you up to consider that certain things were important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Such as?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - we always had to go to Sunday school - and church. Regular attendance at the day school. Oh they insisted on that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did your parents think about swe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - that was taboo.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When grown ups were talking were you children allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If you did something that your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they - might have got a boxed ear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Who would you get that from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Me mother. Me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you get any other sort of punishment at all that you can think of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it just depends - what trouble I were in outside. Might be confined to barracks for about an hour or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Sent to bed would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of offence would you have had to committed to get sent to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it just depends whether I won or lost the fight. And also what mischief we were up to in the park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you get into mischief quite frequently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I did do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So did you get punished quite often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh not at - not - every ti
me we did it. Didn't - took my part sometime. But - like it were - playing football in the streets - and a window were broken I were always one of 'em do you see. We always had to pay our share to the windows. Then in the park the park keeper - he was ver
y - hasty. He always used to come and - always chasing us about. But compared to present day we were angels.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you ever punished by your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you remember any particular occasion which stands out when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well we didn't - we didn't turn in very early one night - so we got punished for that.
