\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, well we did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You managed on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you remember what happened when your younger brother was born - did anybody come into help then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I couldn't remember that. I was only - three and a half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - half a mile away me grandfather and grandmother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was there anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And - their son and daughter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was this on your mother's side or your father's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Your mother side - how much did they see of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well once a week or once a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Where did they see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Our home or their home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents have friends as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they have many?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, not so many - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 A few?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Just a few.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Where did they see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In our home and in their home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your mother and father share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your mother have any friends of her own or your father have his own friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 They were all joint?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were these friends invited into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Occasionally. But it - very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh they'd got for their tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would this be on particular days or particular occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - a particular occasions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would it be birthdays or celebrations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Be something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Would you say that the friends who were invited into the house were your mother's friends or your father's friends or friends of both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 The both of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they call in casually without an invitation ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it'd be very rare if they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about neighbours - did they call in or were they invited into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well that'd be very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would they ever he invited in for a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738 It woul}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 d just be to pass a little time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well their friends but rare - rare - on rare occasions to their friends but not to the neighbours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Not the neighbours at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I daresay they'd have a - a few games and - talking and - I don't know what else they could - what they'd do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of games would they play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well in those days they were dominoes and draughts and ludo, things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they ever have any musical get together}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 with their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You weren't a musical family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Many people divide society into different social classes, in the time prior to 1918 - did you think of some people belonging to one social class and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Those that lived up Chorley New Road and those that - live in - in the slums as they call it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You thought of it as two classes did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you tell me what they were and the people who lived on Chorley New For instance
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well you - you - you could brand them as the employers. We were the workers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You didn't think of any intervening class at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you belonged to the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of people belonged to the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well there was tin mills and engineer works and - and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the employers class - can you think of anybody else who would belong in that category apart from employers?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, the people that was in business. They used to call 'em the - the better class or bet - better class they used to call 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently form people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you ever told to touch your cap or show respect in some way to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, especially the vicar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was there anyone you called Sir or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Only the - the manager of your works when you came in contact with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in any particular way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, everybody that they came in contact with - they give 'em a good name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the district were you lived who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - those that got on the council. The councilors and aldermen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. Not that I know of.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you come into contact with these people at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it might have been at the - election time. That would be all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Why was it that they were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - perhaps its - perhaps they pushed theirself forward.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the shopkeepers - who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they would have friends of their own wouldn't they - in the trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would they have friends out of the trade do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, I daresay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they associate with their customers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well over the counter - only over the counter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Who would the clergy associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 All the parishioners.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 As personal friends would they include the parishioners or any particular group of their parishioners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I don't think they would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Who do you think they would have as their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Other vicars. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You can't think of any other group they would associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the teachers - who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they had - they had the teachers union, they'd associate with - the other teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would they associate with anybody else who wasn't a teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I think they mostly - teachers with teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And employers - would they associate with other employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Anybody else as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it would - it would have to be in the employers line.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were there any farmers about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Any what? Farmers? Just outside the - outside of Bolton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Not in your area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of people would you say went to the church - the church that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they were all classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would you have employers represented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And teachers and professional people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, it was open to any - anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the non-conformist churches - the chapels, do you know what sort of people would go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I expect the same groups.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You don't think it would necessarily be a richer or a poorer group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the Roman Catholic church - what sort of people would go there? There was a Roman Catholic church in the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Well they - all the people that were Catholics would be there whether they were rich or poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you know if there was any friction between the Catholics and the Church of England people in the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. They used to get on very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the p
articular area where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say that there were different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh there - there were different groups.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would you like to say something about that - could you describe a family from the different sorts of groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well - if they got the same wage some would use it differently than others. We say - some went drinking out - every night - they'd be a different category from the people that don't go out. A
nd you can tell it in their homes. Show the difference in their homes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You mean by the standard of furniture?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Or the way it's kept?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about eating - would the people who spent their money on drink perhaps not feed their families so well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 They'd neglect 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 They'd neglect them in relation to clothes as well would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. That's right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 The whole range in fact?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your mother and father - have the same attitude to people in the different groups - different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I - they just took it as other people took it that there was - high classes and the lower classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would they adopt the same attitude to people who squandered their money away on drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh they didn't believe in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they associate with such people at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you think that any one group within the working class felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well there may have been some. Those that push theirself on like to be a councilor or - or any positions that's knocking around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right. Yes. Oh you got a lot of that. You could - you could pick 'em out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 By the way they dressed or spoke or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Spoke and dressed and how they - created. How they - acted and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were there any sort of scenes in the streets or anything like that with the rougher types?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well just depend what district you was in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In your district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no, I couldn't say there were much of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you remember there being a distinction being felt between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Oh yes, remember that quite well because the craftsmen - he had to go to the Technical 
school two or three nights a week and work for little wages. And they were kind of jealous of the information and the knowledge that they got. And those that - didn't care about education and that, they were in the lower group - the labourers. But now the
re's not as much of that now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Things are evening out a bit aren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you think that your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. No, just the ordinary type of the people that - she lived against. The - majority of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would you say that it was possible at that time to move out of one class into another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it was - it was - it did happen but it was very rare. For instance if the lower class had had some money left 'em then they started 
going up there. That's the only way that I saw it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you remember anybody who did move that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No one in particular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you remember anybody being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Who or what sort of person would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - like the - see the Mayor of Bolton years ago. Or a certain doctor or a - councilor. Or you meet 'em in that - in those classes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it was the nature of these people. What they called - they'd do anybody a good turn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you remember seeing a policeman round where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - as young kiddies we used to fly when we saw one. Yes - but they don't now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you ever have any dealings with a policeman when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your mother ever threaten you that she'd call a policeman if you were naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She might have done. She might have done but I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would you take it seriously or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How do you think that the policeman treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well it just depends who they were dealing with. I say, these drunks - they give them something to be going on with. They took - they treated 'em rough. Well they had to tr
eat 'em rough - you see when it took - say, six policeman to lock one man up and - carry him - had to treat him rough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about other kinds of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh he treated - the policeman treated - general people all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You said your home was rented didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you ever see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well he was very good landlord. He was very good. He used to do repairs and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that you paid a reasonable rent for the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they always had to make - struggle to make ends meet. You see, the wages were so poor. The engineer
s wages were only - twenty-three shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And your father was a gas meter inspector?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Gas meter inspector. But there - there's only thirty shillings a week. Now they're about thirteen pound.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you think about this struggle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well it - it was there. I mean to say, if you got a shilling advance in your - in - what you work, you wouldn't get another for six month - or twelve month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you remember your father being off work ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no, well I think he was off - once, that was all. But he got his wage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you ever get financial help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 From any source?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you given lessons at all by either of your parents before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, we went very young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About four year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When you first started what time of the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About quarter to twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about afternoon school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Two o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 'Til}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 ?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Half past four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you go all day when you were four years old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I should think we'd go half a day for first. And then round about four you'd go full time then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you start full time or part time school when you were four?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I think it was part time at four and at five full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What kind of a school was it - was it a board school or a private school or a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, it was a - it was St James - Church of England school. In Waterloo Street.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 It would be a day school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was it just boys or mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 We walked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About how long would it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Six or seven minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well when
 I was young. When we were young mother used to go with us but when we got - about six year old we used to go with all the other children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Where did you have your midday meal then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 We went home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you think about school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh I liked it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well there were some good and - as I liked and others - they didn't appeal to us. I mean it's over a number of years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was there any particular one that you disliked perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I wouldn't say I disliked 'em but - I didn't like 'em us much as the - some of the others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your teachers emphasi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 e certain things as being important - like manners or tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, you had to - line up every morning in the school yard. Looki
ng at - it were clogs in those days - looking at your clogs whether they were clean or not and - looked at the front and looked at the back. Oh yes. And if you were dirty well - go and have a wash.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about manners - did they bother much about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, had to have manners, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were they keen on you being punctual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, they used to get prizes for being punctual.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you get any punishment if you weren't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No - unless you was late pretty often you'd have to go in the schoolmaster's - office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were they concerned at all about the way you spoke?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 They didn't bother about that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, they didn't bother about - that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If you did something that they disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well i
t just depends what it - what you did. You were sent to the schoolmaster. And if it was something serious - over the table and the cane was there. Oh - they punish you. The schoolmaster did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did any of the ordinary teachers punish you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Ah there was one - but it were all on the hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was that with a cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Yes. A cane, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they have any other sort of punishment like sending you out of the classroom or standing in a corner or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, the - 
any punishment that way it was - writing certain words out so many times. Stay in after the class you see until you've finished it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did the girls get the same punishments as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No, they get - they got, now if you do it again you know what'll happen - but that never happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were they not caned at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of offences would you be punished for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they didn't allow talking in the class for one thing. That was one offence. And if the te
acher of the class was away for a few minutes and - somebody took a piece of chalk at the - at the board - and they were caught - that was another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you ever get punished for bad work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 It was just for behaviour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You misbehaved and you got punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. 'Course you had to do homework and all. When we got to - old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they help you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did they visit the school on any occasion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Only when it was a prize distribution - once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would both your mother and father go to that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I don't think so - I think me mother went, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would she go every time she had the chance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Only when the prize distribution was on in the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But each time there was the prize distribution did she go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did she meet the teachers at all? To talk about your progress and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
No. They hadn't that system then as they have - as they have now. You - there was no, take this paper to your parents and - let 'em have a look at it and sigh it. None of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 There was no contact at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Between the parent and the teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
It was less between the - the teacher and the schoolmaster. He - we used to have test examinations every so often and they all went to the - they all finished up at the schoolmaster and he
 used to give you marks for this and marks for that. You knew which was the one you were failing in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did the other children attending the school come from similar types of home to yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Oh yes, all around Waterloo Street and Blackburn R
oad and that - bottom of Blackburn Road and Blackbank Street - they were all of the same type.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well they were - say one of the girls say, she was pretty good at s
inging. Then there was another good at reciting. Well if there were any concerts they were - picked out for 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well you couldn't say gangs, there might be - no more than three. You couldn't call that a gang could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Little groups of friends you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 There was no sort of ganging up together against one another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were there any children who seemed to be left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I think they were pretty fair all round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you go on to another school after that - one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I finished there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You stayed at the same one all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How old were you when you finished?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. The half time system was going then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you left at twelve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Twelve and went half time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And then you finished altogether at thirteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What did you feel about the half time system?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well it varied - at one week you worked at - in the afternoon and the next week you worked at the morning. Well it broke you in - you didn't get as fed up as you would have done if you'd started full time. Only - it was a big pull to be
 there at six o'clock in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you attend any part time education after you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. The Technical school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What course was it that you did there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Cotton spinning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What was that - three evenings a week or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well - one night we'd have say cotton spinning and then - say threequarters of an hour and then we'd go in another room for engineering. That'd be - well we had it on three nights a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was it a specially course for cotton spinners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Oh that was special for - for cotton spinning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And the engineering would be textile engineering?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And engineeri}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738 ng - yes. That was in a - Lower}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738  Bridgman Street. The - and the Wood Technical school that we used to go in the daytime was in Mawdsley Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You went in the daytime as well as in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 That was for woodwork. One half day - well, a couple of hours that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 During the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you released from work to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, no, when we went to the - the there we went from school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 That was before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You had woodwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Woodwork. And then we - some selected woodwork but I didn't, I selected engineering. And that brought cotton spinning in to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You mean you were doing some sort of metal work while you were at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Oh no. No, were just this - this woodwork. And then when - started working then I took these other courses then of - cotton spinning and engineering. I used to go to the Central High Grade in Mawdsley Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 In the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was this for a City and Guilds course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Not a National Certificate or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no, City and guilds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you carried that through until you got - did you get a -?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I went until I was twenty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of a qualification did you get at the end of it - it would be a City and Guilds certificate of some sort wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I got the - no, I didn't get the City and Guil
ds, I don't think so - I - it was the education - certificates that they got there - education committee certificates. And then we - if we put so many attendances in - certain percentage of attendance - and we got certain marks for our homework we got - o
ur fees paid. Fees and all - all books. 'Course the firm paid part of that. Just depends which; course you were taking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Your firm supported you on the course did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. But it - but you didn't get your books at the beginning. You had to quali
fy with these attendances and your - and your work - some how or another, if they paid it at - they give you money for your books and that they only went about a month and then they were - excelled.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you do any other courses after you'd left school apart from that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you think you benefited from attending the evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Oh yes, because it - for the evening classes it's altogether different from what you had in the day school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 It would help you to get a better job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 While you were still attending school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Only when you were on the half time system?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, get - used to get two shillings a week. Two shillings a week for fifty-four hours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 The fifty-four hours would include your school attendance and you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well it - that's what they based - they based the - the work - in the engineering trade. I think the - the cotton was slightly higher, but fifty-four hours for the engineering so we had to do half of that when we was working - half time. But when we w
ent full time had to do this fifty-four hours - for five shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 For the fifty-four hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What exactly was this job you had while you were on the half time system?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I was the check boy in the office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 At what sort of a works?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Engineering works - Dobson and Barlow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Me father got it me. Jobs were hard to get at one time but now they're ten a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well the - the firms system was a c
heck system - had three checks. Around one - no, a square - a oblong one for - from six 'til eight then you had a whole one from half past eight until twelve o'clock and then you had a round one from one o'clock until five o'clock. So these checks - when 
t
he men came in they had a box there - with a stand and if it was morning - you'd show - you'd throw your early morning check in. Well - we boys, about three or four of us, we had to stand at this 'ere box to see that they put right checks in and if they p
u
t the wrong one we used to shout out but we didn't see everyone and we - when we got 'em in the - in the office, in the back room there was tables and we used to put all these checks on and - sort out all the numbers out and then - when we sorted 'em all 
o
ut in different numbers there was different - what shall I say - different boards with slots in and all these checks was put in - oh you used to get a packet like that you know - when you got used. Well those boards represented different departments so - 
they were checked off by some of the clerks. Then in the afternoon they were sent out back into the shop and - then they had someone in the shop to give 'em out to - to the men all the three checks then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Each man had a different numbered check?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. That's right, yes. Ah - the - the highest number was four thousand and fifty. At Dobson and Barlow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would there be about four thousand workers there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About - about four thousand workers, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You'd got quite a number of cards to sort out hadn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. So they used to call us check boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 One week you worked mornings and the afternoons the next week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you started at six in the morning when it was your morning shift?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What time did you finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
At twelve o'clock. Well we had the - went at eight o'clock and then half - half an hour for breakfast and then we went until twelve o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And the week when you worked afternoons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 One - one until five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you work on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Fifty-four hour week it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the week when you were working one 'til five - did you work on Saturday that week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I think we changed on the Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And worked the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. And then the week after was
 on - we did - we'd be on on the mornings. I think it was Saturday we changed. No, we didn't change on Saturday - that was the end of the week - was Saturday. So we changed on the Monday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So did you get the alternate Saturday morning off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. When it was half time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh didn't have - no work on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have any holidays while you were on the half time system?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, when Bolton used to have - about four days at Whitsuntide but we would have - the firm would close down you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would this be paid or unpaid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - no pay then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You were paid two shillings for your proportion of the week that you put in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that that was a fair wage as wages went at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well it - it wasn't enough. And then when we went - see the system in the - in the office, check boys was - there was - two full time and three half timers. That's how worked it so - when it came our turn to jump up to full time we got four
 shillings. Then when I'd been there so long - was drafted into the works then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You told me that you got a penny in the shilling back from your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. That was a regular - a regular scale that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you got that while you were working as a half timer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you actually give the money as whole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, you paid everything up then we got - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 To your mother or your father?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And it was she who gave you the penny back was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What was it spent on - the money that you paid to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What do you mean, the wage? Oh it went - in the housekeeping money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you get on with the other people in the check office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - very good except one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was that one of the full timers or the half timers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
He was a - we were both half times and you see the - we used to have to - the half timers used to have to go out into the - engineering works yard against the gates when the men were coming in
 - and the half timers used to have to - they had to go out five minutes before the full timers. Why that was so, these half timers caught the first crowd going in - but you wanted all the lot on - on duty when the rush came at - at the last minute. Well 
-
 one day there were two of us - been having a bit of an argument and one were a bit taller than me and he struck out at me so - we - we had a set-to in the - in the back place of the office. Well happened these here men were coming in they - they had a dr
a
were like where the checks dropped through a slot. Well we had to go out and put the drawer in, well we hadn't put that drawer in. And - the boss in the office was a very big stout chap he - he come in and he - we were like two niggers. We'd been rolling 
on t' floor. And he give us another dose. Get out vonder. Anyway that - that settled it. We were all right after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it just depended how - I was in several departments. Now the first department as I went in after leaving the check office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 While you were still in the check office how did they treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - they kept us under - that's when he came and he - he - he give us another dose after we'd been hitting one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 He was very strict with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well didn't - make any difference. Oh no, we thought, oh well, it's him - he has to - give us so much punishment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh I liked the work all right. Oh ye
s. See - sooner you - quicker you did the job - 'course at first you're like this here - you know - when you get used you have 'em in your hand - like that, it's about the same as on the typewriter you know - slow at the beginning. Sooner you got 'em in y
our boards and then you're finished. You had to sit down like in the - back place and if there's any errands wanted doing - any messaged to the - upstairs in the office or to the works we had to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did having the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. No, because we followed up you see after - going to the technical school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Do you feel that you were really too tired to get the benefit of school that last year?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - when you - when we started full time - it was quite a drag - they were long days then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
But while you were still part time, going to work and going to school as well, did you feel that your schoolwork suffered because you were working or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No - it was - would to to a certain extent but - we got in the 
top class so - we didn't really miss so much from - the syllabus - we could do it from the syllabus. And then - one of the jobs that we had, our headmaster was a for - partner in a printing works - Waddington and Jackman, School Hill and - and Herne Hill 
L
ondon and school Hill Bolton and they used to print the examination papers - arithmetic examination - all sums and that. And they used to be printed - draught copies at his works and then he used to bring 'em to the school. Well - us in the top class we u
sed to have to check these off. We used to get a penny a mistake. Sometimes there were some mistakes and sometimes there weren't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh it was - picnic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You liked it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you do any other part time job at all before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was your first full time job at Dobson and Barlow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you get it by virtue of being there already?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it was a - when you got - thirteen - fourteen it was your turn to mo
ve out - out of the time place so - they picked - they got you a job or you - sometimes you got it yourself. But sometimes the foreman'd come round and say, have you any boys ready for - moving out? Well the first job that I had - from the time place was 
a
 - a job that - the apprentices today won't believe it - but the last place as I worked at when I retired the - there was a fore - a foreman there and he was a boy when I was a boy and he used to tell the boys as worked under him how much we got. And he s
a
id, now just go and see Jimmy, see what he tells you. And it were the same thing. We got five shillings a week and we had to mind ten automatic wheel cutting machines. That was a penny an hour - well about a penny farthing an hour. That's ten machines - w
a
s five on each side. We got a - we got five shillings a week for minding those machines. So that's where the profit was coming to the employer. And that charge hand if he saw - if you was at - on this side and there was a boy on the other side - if he saw
 you talking he'd come there and - oh there was a lot of that in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Slapping you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Yes. Oh yes, but - back of the neck or - in fact - occasionally in some of the shops. I didn't get it, but - they used to - get punched. Oh yes. Just depends on the - whether }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6228345\charrsid11173738 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
 were narky fellows or not. You met some all right but - others he were a tarter. This one as used go come and box your ears - he had a machine and it - it traveled so long and he's looking over top you know at these'ere lads see wheth
er they're talking or what. I never forget that place. I - I used to call it ten a penny job. So those that work now they - they won't believe that we - we had to - had to mind so many machines for a penny an hour. Oh yes, I didn't care for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you working six in the morning 'til five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you had half hour for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Yes. And - an hour for dinner. And there were no canteen or anything, you had to - had to go home. And those that lived up Blackburn Road and Halliw
ell Road - I think went to Hesketh Street and the other went to - Tramway. There was a firm down Brige Street. Edmond Holden - Edmond Holdens cab yard. That's what - it was that at the first - that's where they - Palladium is or - that wrestling place. We
l
l I think there's some bother about a garage now but it - it was registered as a cab yard so - those are after a garage will be able - they'll have a good pull. Anyway they used to have wagoneettes - open wagonettes. Charge you a penny up and a penny down
.
 So you could go up to Hesketh Street or Astley Street for tuppence and then you - you're dinner - dinner was waiting for you when you got home. But those were - as were near - oh used to see 'em running. Especially for the half hour. This 'ere five minut
es run home, five minutes back you've only twenty minutes for your breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you always go home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Or did you sometimes take sandwiches?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, always - always home, there's not - there's no canteens at all. If you - the shop t
hat I went in fitting after - if the foreman saw you eating an apple he - he'd send for you. You're paid to work here, not eat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you not allowed to eat on the premises?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 During the mealtimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. Oh no. Unless you - open your drawer and just nibble at something and - had your eye round where the foreman was but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you work on Saturdays when you were full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Saturday mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. But - later - we went on the - eight o'clock system. Starting at e
ight o'clock. They did away with the six to eight but we had to - we had to work a bit longer - and then round about that time you was lucky if you did work full time. Trade was bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When would this be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 19 - 1913. From - last week in November 19
13 until the seventeenth of March - 1914, we was on strike. We had no strike pay. And then - the war broke out the same year, 1914, and - all the engineering firms bucked up then but - I've known people that worked at Dobson and Barlows, I've known 'em to
 - when they've been s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1973345\charrsid11173738 ick}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
 I've known 'em to - to play 'em twelve month and then when they've gone after a job, say they got a order in - in the shop, foreman'd send for 'em and they're out of work again in three month. There was a lot of that. These that ar
e working in engineering works now they - they only don't - those that commencing during the war they've only know prosperity. We didn't - we knew more short time than anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were you yourself on short time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, all the shop went on short time but - I didn't get as much short time as some of the others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You worked six 'til five and Saturday mornings 'til twelve until you went onto this eight o'clock?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What time did you finish then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh it wasn't eight o'clock. It 
were half past seven. Aye, half past seven. And then we - that would six - an hour and a half wouldn't it. Well we had to gain that you see, quarter hour twenty minutes each day to make - the time - I think we came on forty-seven hours. Now it's a - it's 
forty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have the Whit holiday when you were working full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Oh yes, but then there was only - it was in August, third Saturday in August and we just had four days. And then it was - few years after that when they came on for - for a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About when would it be that they had a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Just previous to 1910.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was it still unpaid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no pay - no pay for - no work no pay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that the money you were paid was a fair wage or not at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well in 19 - 1913, that strike was - we wanted two shilling a week extra - but didn't get it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 On top of your four shillings was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. The - the rate was thirty-three shillings a week for engineering fitters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You'd moved on to being a fitter then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you go onto the new hours when you became a fitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Oh yes. I - we - we weren't on the new hours when I - when I - when I worked in the - on the machines. When I got in the shop a few years after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What were you paid while you were minding the machines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Five - five shillings. For fifty-four hours. And we used to mind ten - ten automatic machines - wheel cutting machines.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you were given a penny in the shilling yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. From - from - from mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you get on with the other people in the machine shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh, got on very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Apart from the charge}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1973345\charrsid11173738  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 hands or foremen being strict how did you feel that the employer treated you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - the managing director was Rushton - he was called
 the old chap but - it was very seldom you saw him. But if you - if you did see him in any of the departments there was something going to be done drastic. I mean, cut - cut this out or cut that out and - they had a - they had a man going round - called h
i
m Speedycut. Testing all the - checking all the jobs off, timing them with a stopwatch and then - the prices - it were piece work on a lot of the jobs in the fitting job and - he was - timing you how long it took different jobs and what money got for it a
n
d then that'd go in the office and then next thing - a drop in piece work prices. But - so you never saw much of the - of the old chap. Now he - he had a son and he was a very - well, he died did the old chap. They lived at Halliwell Lodge. Then - the you
n
ger one - 'course they used to call him Young Jimmy but - he was a - he got an old chap and the only time that - the only time that I recollect him coming in to our fitting shop was - the day - 1914 - they first knew the war broke out. He came down to - t
o
 tell us that - all the - all the orders in the shop were foreign so therefore that would stop. There'd be no work in the shop. So he said, they wanted men in the shopyard. So - the same night fif - fifty of us from Bolton went up - to the Clyde - River C
l
yde in Scotland in the shipyard and - the war broke out, I think it - I think it was the - eleven o'clock that same morning or else it was the morning after we was in Scotland then when it broke out. So that's the only time that I remember seeing this - t
his managing director. But - the manager himself, of the works, he used to come round to foremen - see about progress.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 He didn't bother with you - only foremen. Aye they used to - lads'd - they, she - manager's here. And - pht.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about the work when you were in the machine shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh I'd left the machine shop then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, but when you - were still in the machine shop how did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh I didn't care much for it. Too monotonous. The same ten machines every day you went in and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about when you became a fitter - when exactly did you become a fitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Be about fifteen. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What were you paid then as a fitter? Thirty three shillings was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, not appren
tice - were only apprentice. Apprentice from - I was apprentice from fifteen to twenty-one. Fifteen you got - six shillings. Sixteen you got seven. Seventeen you got eight. Nineteen - nineteen you got - eleven. And at twenty you got thirteen - thirteen sh
illing when you were twenty. They're giving school children more than that for spending money now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You still gave the money to your mother did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you still get a penny in the shilling back or did it increase at all as you were earning more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it - might have increased a bit but - I didn't take much out because me - me father had died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When you were working as a fitter, when you'd finished your apprenticeship, what were you paid then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well the rate for the job was thirty-three shillings but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But then they went on piece work did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
No. No, that was thirty-three shillings but - for a full fitter's wage but - you - you got - you wasn't classed as a full fitter when you come twenty-one. Instead of get - being paid at twenty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You weren't classes as a full fitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
You'd serve you - you - you'd serve your seven years apprenticeship but you didn't - come on to what they called full money when you were twenty-one. The - they - basically it wa
s thirty-three shillings but they paid you twenty-four. Only got twenty-four shillings when you became twenty-one. And then - you were supposed to get a shilling rise every three month.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Until it got up to thirty-three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, if you were lucky. S
ee, you might have been in that period when it was a slack period and then you had to lay off, so they expected you to make - make that period up. And then when you came twenty-one - came - when you came twenty-three, that was two years after twenty-one, 
y
ou were expected to get full money, but - you'd go to the foreman, say I'm twenty-three. Oh he says, we can't pay you any more, you'd better take a week's notice. That was a regular thing at Dobson and Barlows. So - a rule in the society was if you went t
o another firm they had to pay you full money. So the majority of Dobson and Barlows went to a - Barrow-in-Furness, in a shipyard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about the work as a fitter - did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, I enjoyed it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you get on with the other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh champion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You went up to the Clyde when the war broke out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that was August 1914.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you stay working up there or did you come back to Bolton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No up to - what we did - we worked on the torpedo de
stroyers at Yarrows. And we worked there from August until - Christmastime. Then we came home for our holiday. Just the weekend. But in Scotland - they worked at Christmas but they had - ten days in - new year. While we was there they agreed to just have 
t
he - a week, not ten days. But we came - we came back on this weekend for Christmas and we - we - we heard of another job at Chatham dockyard - down south. And it was a - it was about that time when - a few years after when they introduced the forty-seven
 
hours for - for Bolton but the - Chatham dockyard with being a government depot they worked forty-seven hours and we got a pound a - a pound a week subsistence money, that was to pay for your - for your lodgings. So we went down there because we - all as 
we got when we went to Scotland was a - thirty-seven shillings a week and you had to - pay digs there and send some money home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What were you actually doing in the shipyard - were you working as a fitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Both in Scotland and Chatham?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, we were - down at Chatham was on the - submarine work. But was all fitting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you feel about the work in the shipyard compared with Dobson and Barlow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well it was - it were different work. Oh it was an experience. There was a - a
bout eight or nine month we would be there. And Dobson and Barlow got - some government contracts. For Army Field Kitchens so they sent for - us - for us back. See, they had no men - so they sent for us back. At first we didn't - we wouldn't come back. Bu
t then they sent a threatening letter that - if we didn't come back then they'd - we couldn't claim Dobson and Barlows as our - as our firm. See, we was kind of loaned to the shipyard so when the war - well people expected th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1973345\charrsid11173738 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 n that the war'd be finished in
 about two month. Went on for years. So we came back and worked at making Army field kitchens. And in between we was making - machines to make - to turn - bomb shells and all that. It was all war work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 When you were working for the shipyards how did you feel that you were treated then by the employers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Oh well - they were - they couldn't get hold of enough men so they had to lean to 'em you see. Oh the - well I did very well in - in Scotland but - well, they call 'em chargehand but actually fore
men at Yarrow. He wanted me to stop up there but we heard about this other job so went down to Chatham. We were there until - oh we had a nice chargehand there. I was there until - Dobson and Barlow sent for us back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you stay at Dobson and Barlows all your working life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. I worked for Dobson and Barlows - thirty-three years. The last - the last three and a half years I - I worked in the cost office.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you do any other jobs between being a fitter and going into the cost office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Oh no. No. Then - the firm closed. And - I went back on the bench - at Bradley Fold. Weren't there so long, there were only a few working there - they'd no work in. And then I went from there to - Fine Spinners. I worked - I worked there seventeen years.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What were you doing there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I was a chargehand - chargehand over fitters. And I worked there seventeen years - seventeen years and then I retired in 1953.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would you have preferred any other type of occupation than being a fitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, I don't know as I would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. A.E.U.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you take part in any of its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well, for a short period I - I was a cheque book keeper, that was all, perhaps for about two years. I never was
 Secretary, Treasurer, anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You were the check book keeper - do you mean you collected the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Used to have about three on a table you see and the Secretary used to sign the book when the money was paid in - and the check book 
keeper he was on - he was checking against the - the Secretary. Then the - the other check book keeper was the one that drew the money then booked it down then he - put it over to the other check book keeper. Checking the money off as it was paid in. But 
the Secretary, he always marked your cards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that your employers had the same interests at the workers or different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - at certain periods - they didn't take their interest in - on the sporting side same as I do now. If 
you - stayed off to go to a football match or athletic match, anything like that - you either layed off for several days or you were sacked. But now all these firms encourage - sport.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was there any welfare scheme of any kind at Dobson and Barlow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 At any time while you worked there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
No, if you got - I got that finger hit when I was fourteen - trapped in one of these ten machines. The ambulance man, he had to be - they had to send for him. He was - a couple of blocks away and he - he
 worked on a machine and he had to wash his hands before he come and - he doctored you up but - now they have a proper welfare system. Oh there was no welfares then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that there was any sort of friction between the employers and the workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well there were when we had that - I was in four - four lock outs and four - on strikes. And - a lock out is when the firm said - you're finished. A strike when the - the man ballot to come out and they just say, we're finished. I was in about - 
I was in four of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What were these about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Wages. And conditions. Wages and conditions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of things were you bothered about as far as conditions were concerned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well this - piecework system, dropping the prices - that was on
e. And - on the other hand workers wanted an advance. So neither - neither would agree so - sometimes there were lock outs sometimes a strike. Then the men would - appoint a committee and they'd bring all the points up that - comes from the floor of - the
 
shop. They - they had a representative from each shop. Then - he'd take it to the meeting. I know on - time there was a meeting they had ten complaints so then that goes to the union and he goes to see the - the management. But the management was - that y
o
u know - but now - the management used to run the works - and rule the men. But now it's other way round - it's the unions that are - they're ruling the works in a sense with the shop stewards and - they have shop stewards doing nothing, only shop steward
. But in those days - you were fright - you were frightened of being made a shop - a shop steward because any short time you were the first to go. The first to go and - your noise goes then. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was all the negotiating carried out with the manageme
nt by the shop stewards in the firm or was there somebody from the office in town who would negotiate with the management for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well the - the un - if it was official - the union - the union office - the district secretary called a meeting of the 
district committee so they did the negotiating. I'll not say all the district committee - there might have been sent deputation, about three or four. But on the other hand - there'd be the man - there'd be manager of the works and the - employers Federati
on Secretary. So it were those that conducted the - arrangements. Then they all reported back to their - unions and if it didn't suit well - continue the strike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were the strikes that you were involved in official or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 They were official strikes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. Well the strike was official but the - the lock out, that was official rom the - other side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest amongst the workers themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, they - seeing there were - they had their numbers working there they - they practically stood by one another - any disputes and that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about the division between the trained craftsman and the other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well I think I mentioned in - in a - one of the other reels - I've just
 told you the scale of wages that apprentices got paid, and then you was - you were supposed to go to the night school - night classes. Well if you - if you passed your examinations you got fee - for your books and for your fees. But for the other things 
t
hat you wanted you had to - you had to buy those and you had to buy your own tools, tools of the trade. Well they - about the time the basic was thirty-three shillings a week but - the class that they called the labourers, that's the - just carried the wo
r
k about from shop to shop - their rate was eighteen shillings a week. But now the - come level now. In fact, when you look at the wages these 'ere motor men at - on the road at Horwich - eighty pound a week - they're making and they're - they're - that's 
n
ot a trade. So now they have a sliding scale - every time the - skilled man egts a - an advance the apprentice has so many - so much proportion. Say seventy-five per cent or - just depends what age they are. Now the - the labouring class - is coming up th
e same - but they're moving up quicker.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Did you feel that you as a trained craftsman were in a different sort of category from the labourers in the firm - were you made to feel different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, used to get on with - with the labourers and that but
 - they knew their position. And they knew the system - I mean to say, you - if you read the history of a lot of these trade unions - the labourers are only getting eighteen shillings a week - the Post Office was on - was on a - a low rate. Ah, there's on
e Prime - one - Chancellor of the Exchequer - oh Postmaster General when the - Post Office men went in for an advance, oh he said, the country couldn't pay them. He called them bloodsuckers. So next time as he put up for election out he went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 This was a local M.P. in Bolton wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Yes. Lord Derby. Yes. His name was Stanley before. His name was Stanley - and he was fighting in - in South Africa, the Boer War. And he got in but the next time - he got in good time at Westhoughton but when he came
 out with this statement they never had a Conservative M.P. after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 After you left school you continued to live at home didn't you until you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about your relationship with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 We were all right. Oh yes, we got on very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you spend your Sunday any differently or did you still go on going to Sunday school and church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - I kept on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You've 
already told me a bit about how you spent your spare time - after you left school and were working, when you were about eighteen or nineteen you started going to the theatre and concerts and such like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And then there was the Harriers - did you go out in the evening much apart from the time you spent with the Harriers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. I was out every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What other sorts of things did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well we did a lot of walking. And then we - training for football and running.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Who would you be doing this with - would it be with a club or a group of friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - one was - with the young club. I think I mentioned that before.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you make any new friends about this time after you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes. Those that was in the youth club and - and the football club.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you make any new friends at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were they all boys - the friends that you made at this time, or were there some girls as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - be mostly boys but there were girlfriends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How was it that you met them - was it through the youth club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Through the Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you ever bring your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have any special}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1973345\charrsid11173738  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 friends about that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, not special. Not - not - until I started courting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents meet your friends at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no, I never took 'em home - only when I started courting - take - took me young lady home then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But your parents didn't meet your other friends at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh if you were very late they'd ask you where'd you been. But - majority - majority of times well we - they knew we were in good company.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Just depends what age you were do you see - when you was going to school you had to be in bed be eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 After you'd left school, when you were working, did you have to be home at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh - about ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
 in 1910 weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How long had you known your wife then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh about five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was she a local girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She was Bolton born and bred was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 From the same district?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well she was near - St Johns school and I was near - St James school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But you met at the same youth club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. Not - the youth club was only - boys. But - we met at the St Johns at the Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She came to your Sunday school then
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. That's right. At the day school and all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Even though she lived a bit nearer to the other church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh no. I lived near to the other church. She was - she - she was near St Johns and she went there at Sunday school and day school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And you lived further away but you went to the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 See - I went to St James in the daytime and at the Sunday I went to St Johns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you save up before you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 The little that we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your parents help you in setting up home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, me father was dead. And - me mother died three years after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How long were you actually engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Could you describe the wedding? Who would be there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well - my old lady's - father. Me mother had died. And her brother and her sisters and her brothers children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 And on your side?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 My brother. One uncle and two aunts. Oh no, two - two uncles and three aunts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Not your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She was dead.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Can you remember what you got in the way of wedding presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well there was a lot - like a - a rug and - a - crockery and bedding. Mostly like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have a fair number or not such a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, not - well - you couldn't say it was a - lot in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well if you call two days at Southport a honeymoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 I got the impression that you were on strike when you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738  - is this right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh we - we hadn't been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738  so long when we were on strike. That was 19 - November 1913 to about March 17, 1914. Well we'd been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
 - about two and a half years, something like that. But was on short time when I got - got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You went to live in Huddart Street didn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How long did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Fifty-eight years this month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 This is the house that you've recently had to leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did your wife have a job when you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. No, her mother was - her mother had died and - well, while she was living she - they had a lar
ge family and she kept my - young lady - she was young lady then - at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She looked after the household?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She helped her mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did she do any jobs at all after her marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How do you think she felt about working in her own family as opposed to going out to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 She never grumbled. See the mother died and so - and then several of the - the brother and several sisters had got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738  so had to look after the father then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have any children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How much of your earnings would you give to your wife in the period of your marriage up to 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well, remember when we first got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12404476 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738  I used to have two shillings a week spending money. There's not been so many get that rate nowadays do they. W
ell, it was this way. If you worked a full week you got thirty-three shillings but we didn't work many - many full weeks. And we got - about twenty-four shillings. Well you couldn't take much out of twenty-four shillings could you. And }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1973345\charrsid11173738 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 arry - carry on in the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So if you earned twenty-four shillings you kept two shillings and gave her the twenty-two to run the house on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 How many rooms were there in the house at Huddart Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Three - three up, two down and a pantry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What do you mean by a pantry - do you mean just a place for keeping food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You had three up - were they three bedrooms or two bedrooms and a bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, two - two bedrooms and a attic room but in the attic you could put two full size bed rooms in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Downstairs was it a living room and a kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes, that's right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Were there any relatives or lodgers living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you have any paid help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Would your wife make and mend clothes for you and herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No, she didn't make 'em - she perhaps mended 'em but she didn't make them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 So the clothes would all be bought - new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 New. Well we had to make am last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You didn't buy them very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 No. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 About how often would you have new clothes - a new suit for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Perhaps about eight - eighteen months, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Where would you go to to buy clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 The shops in town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Any particular one or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well there used to be tailor's shop in - Knowsley Street - Smith and Calverts. Used to get me suits from there but - then they closed. I went there a good number of years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about your wife - where would she get her clothes from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well there was a - a dress house on Folds Road and it was some friends of theirs so she got 'em from there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What about shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Well we could - at one period we got most of our shoes from the Co-op.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 But from other shops in town as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Oh yes, if we saw a bargain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you help at all with the jobs in the house - cleaning, cooking, washing, washing up or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 If there was any cleaning to do - but I didn't wash up or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You would sometimes do a bit of cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 What sort of cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 
Well like wiping the paint down and if they wanted painting used to paint 'em over where it - the landlord, he didn't do anything. So you had to do - any repair jobs.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 You had to do the decorating and repairs yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15140853 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Did you make the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604715 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13323940\charrsid11173738 Yes.
